title.rendered: Urvashi Rautela shares cryptic happy birthday wish on Rishabh Pant’s birthday, gives a flying kiss

content.rendered:
Actress Urvashi Rautela, on Tuesday, shared a new video of herself on her Instagram account blowing a flying kiss with the caption, “Happy Birthday.” Although her post did not mention any name, netizens were quick to point out that Urvashi’s cryptic birthday post video was for cricketer Rishabh Pant as her video posting day and wicketkeeper cricketer’s birth on the same day. Several fans asked in the comment section that the video is for Pant, isn’t. A fan joked, “He won’t reply.” Another said, “What is this style of wishing, or proposing.”

Read also:Rohit Sharma becomes fastest captain to win 50 matches in international cricket history and 1st Indian skipper to win a t20 series against south Africa at home
